column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY CHOCOLATE TABLET DAIRY MILK, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210098726
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, cocoa butter, cocoa mass, vegetable fats (palm, shea), emulsifiers (E442, E476), flavourings. Family milk chocolate: Milk solids 20% minimum, Actual 23%. Cocoa solids 20% minimum.Contains vegetable fats in addition to cocoa butter.**The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of family milk chocolate. MAY CONTAIN NUTS AND WHEAT. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 12/08/2016
